<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Cycle parking <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent62e69656de22427193b2df0c77bd7af0">
</div>


		
There is a multi storey car park at the Royal Hallamshire Hospital, which is 5 minutes walk from the Jessop Wing. Parking is limited and we therefore advise that you leave plenty of time before your appointment to find a parking space. 

Parking at the Jessop Wing is also very limited.  
